name: Blockbench 3D Model
summary: A BBMODEL file is a project created by Blockbench, an open-source 3D model editor. It contains JSON-like plain text information about a 3D model and may include one or more .PNG or .TGA textures. Blockbench users save projects as BBMODEL files when creating and modifying 3D models for people, creatures, animals, and objects.
